  "general_provisions": "This bill reduces the motor fuel tax rate, requires reporting related to refining operations, and enacts provisions related to pipeline permitting.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>enacts provisions related to permitting and right-of-way coordination for certain oil and gas infrastructure;<hr><ltbullet>reduces the rate of the motor fuel tax;<hr><ltbullet>requires refineries to report to the Office of Energy Development regarding production;<hr><ltbullet>provides guidelines regarding information and data reported by refineries to the Office of Energy Development;<hr><ltbullet>amends definitions related to the High Cost Infrastructure Development Tax Credit; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical changes.",
